name: go-apicurio-sdk

name: algorythmix
description: Represents an app for financial asset management and trading called "Algorythmix". The app is intended for non-commercial use. Algorythmix includes features like asset and portfolio tracking and management, financial analysis, and trading. This repository acts like a monorepo for the system based on an event-driven microservices architecture.
